title: Obama stumps for Sen. Murray in Washington state
text: Photo: Pablo Martinez Monsivais, AP President Barack Obama with Sen. Patty Murray, D-Wash., during a democratic fundraiser in Seattle, Friday, Oct. 9, 2015. Obama attended the fundraiser event for Murray and he is also attending fundraisers this weekend in San Francisco and Los Angeles as part of a four-day West Coast tour.
